Compilation
-----------
$ g++ WriteTest.cpp -o WriteTest
$ g++ AntColony.cpp -o AntColony
$ g++ GA_Normal.cpp -o GA_Normal
$ g++ GA_Optimal.cpp -o GA_Optimal
$ g++ DP.cpp -o DP
$ javac TSP.java

Usage
-----
Create an input file Graph.INP containing the coordinates of points in the range [800, 600] and number of points is 60:
$ ./WriteTest 800 600 60

Run Ant Colony algorithm. Input: Graph.INP. Output: AntColony.OUT
$ ./AntColony

Run Genetic Algorithm. Input: Graph.INP. Output: GA.OUT
$ ./GA_Normal
or
$ ./GA_Optimal

Visualize the solution for Ant Colony algorithm. Output image: AntColony.bmp
$ java TSP AntColony

Visualize the solution for Genetic algorithm. Output image: GA.bmp
$ java TSP GA
